ins/wp-twilio-core/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WP Twilio Core WordPress plugin</a> (free) installed (1.2.0+).</li>\n 	<li>You must be using woocommerce on your website .</li>\n 	<li>You must have created a Mobile Number question (text field) and made sure it appears on the registration forms.</li>\n</ol>\";s:17:\"short_description\";s:111:\"Send SMS notifications to the admin phone number everytime there is a job submitted.More features are included.\";s:10:\"banner_url\";s:61:\"//s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/freemius/plugins/7231/banner.png\";s:15:\"card_banner_url\";s:66:\"//s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/freemius/plugins/7231/card_banner.png\";s:15:\"selling_point_0\";s:37:\"Increase your Job Board\'s engagement.\";s:15:\"selling_point_1\";s:63:\"Satisfy your customers showing them that you are on their back.\";s:15:\"selling_point_2\";s:54:\"Provide a Top-notch reminder and notification service.\";s:11:\"screenshots\";N;s:2:\"id\";s:4:\"1912\";s:7:\"updated\";N;s:7:\"created\";s:19:\"2020-11-16 07:22:43\";s:22:\"\0FS_Entity\0_is_updated\";b:0;}s:10:\"is_premium\";b:0;s:14:\"premium_suffix\";s:9:\"(Premium)\";s:7:\"is_live\";b:1;s:10:\"public_key\";s:32:\"pk_02c0f76dc629d8411153d2a7847d9\";s:10:\"secret_key\";N;s:2:\"id\";s:4:\"7231\";s:7:\"updated\";s:19:\"2020-11-17 07:23:30\";s:7:\"created\";s:19:\"2020-11-16 06:43:45\";s:22:\"\0FS_Entity\0_is_updated\";b:0;s:22:\"premium_releases_count\";i:1;s:9:\"bundle_id\";N;s:17:\"bundle_public_key\";N;}}}s:13:\"admin_notices\";a:1:{s:14:\"wp-twilio-core\";a:0:{}}}', 'yes');
